{"tid":560964,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"英國留學吹水區 2月號","createTime":"2018-02-14T14:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T23:12:20.000Z","uid":27766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c39bd5d2ebba2001254ca4b6f905057e535766fe","tid":560964,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"簡介: <br />\n希望為各位喺英國留學嘅朋友開個位吹吓水、相認等等...同時希望提供少少英國留學嘅資訊。另外，仲有LIHKG 英國留學whatsapp group，有興趣請inbox<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Registration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRegistration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=963b3e82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Registration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749</a><br />\n舊group2，3有興趣都請pm<br />\n<br />\n資訊區: <br />\n俗稱[大台] UK Uni secret: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ukunisecrets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fukunisecrets&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4e1cc6cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ukunisecrets</a><br />\n<br />\nHK-UK Student Network<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkukstudentnet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkukstudentnet%2F&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b7042c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkukstudentnet/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國本土學生討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestudentroom.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestudentroom.co.uk&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=54b2de63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestudentroom.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n大學排名:<br />\nThe Complete University Guide <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4e722a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nQS<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.topuniversities.com/qs-world-university-rankings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.topuniversities.com%2Fqs-world-university-rankings&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=56ab4505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.topuniversities.com/qs-world-university-rankings</a><br />\n<br />\n購物:<br />\n基乎所以生活所需二手用品都可以喺呢度搵到<br />\n租屋都得<br />\nGumtree:<br />\n<a href=\"http://guntree.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguntree.com&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c6790748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">guntree.com</a><br />\n<br />\n二手車 Autotrader:<br />\n<a href=\"http://autotrader.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fautotrader.co.uk&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d60b987c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">autotrader.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nHot uk deals: <br />\n<a href=\"http://hotukdeals.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotukdeals.com&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f460b973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotukdeals.com</a><br />\n<br />\n租屋:<br />\nZoopla: <br />\n<a href=\"http://zoopla.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzoopla.co.uk&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d7b43ae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zoopla.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nRightmove:<br />\n<a href=\"http://rightmove.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frightmove.co.uk&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=24aab388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rightmove.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n問答區:<br />\n<br />\n生活區:<br />\nQuestion: 同人夾屋住，rent+bills多數喺咩range？<br />\nANS: 總結個人及身邊朋友既經驗，同人合租租金大約400至500英鎊一個月(視乎地區、大細、幾多個人夾) ；Studio租金則完全基於地區，中北部可以低至600英鎊，倫敦可以貴到3000英鎊一個月，bills 大約一個人50英鎊一個月(都係視乎地區、使用量、租住單位既類型等) ，以上數字均為個人建議，一切以閣下最後合約作準，本人不負任何法律責任。<br />\n<br />\nQuestion: 第一次去英國 有咩要注意？<br />\nAns: 第一次去英國帶少啲嘢去，啱啱好23kg就夠，基本上英國乜都有得賣。<br />\n<br />\nIELTS:<br />\nQuestion: IELTS係咪必須?<br />\nANS: 唔係，某d情況下，例如閣下UKAL 英文成績或HKDSE英文成績理想，可以獲得豁免。但請各位以你地既學校既要求作準。<br />\n<br />\nQuestion: 普通ielts定係UKVI ielts？<br />\nANS: 依家多數都需要UKVI，但詳細可以send個email俾uni問下。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n如有錯漏，請留言指正。會喺3月號post 改正，謝謝。"},{"pid":"4e12185541a5d96c5e193714ab517471c9cd9d3d","tid":560964,"uid":49945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"Ncl lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1955e113765458405d78877b84370d4f2750b02","tid":560964,"uid":17598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"有無人讀緊sussex media and communication<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbad91d2a231f22c9a646a0a4d4d92ebb7ec6c9","tid":560964,"uid":78327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"ielts 炒左writing 應唔應該照send 成績過去英國先？定直接再考過比較好？"},{"pid":"b8ef3b2ecb729db3edc04f016ad61d1b0d1547a8","tid":560964,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T20:29:25.000Z","msg":"想問Birmingham civil 點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa829652b222fffa7ec2b1bfcbe84043f46d936","tid":560964,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:14:44.000Z","msg":"sussex 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867e51c7a742ab8e8782689e10eedeae550b7176","tid":560964,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1955e113765458405d78877b84370d4f2750b02","tid":560964,"uid":17598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"有無人